WEBVTT

00:00:03.627 --> 00:00:07.838
"Osjetih pogreb, u svom mozgu,

00:00:07.838 --> 00:00:10.240
a žalobnici uzvrzmani

00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:12.900
gaze - i gaze - sve dok ne bi osjetio

00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:15.836
k'o da moj um se probi van.

00:00:15.836 --> 00:00:17.605
A kad su sjeli, svi,

00:00:17.605 --> 00:00:19.603
obred je poput bubnja

00:00:19.603 --> 00:00:22.315
stao da bije, bije, sve dok ne osjetih

00:00:22.315 --> 00:00:25.831
da moja pamet obamrije

00:00:25.831 --> 00:00:27.707
A kada čuh da kovčeg dižu

00:00:27.707 --> 00:00:29.994
i kroz dušu mi škripe

00:00:29.994 --> 00:00:33.053
one iste olovne čizme, opet,